 et al [EMP]. This code integrates into a single                  8131 1451
 system a number of important modules and features:               8131 1451
                                                                  8131 1451
 - Spherical and deformed Optical Model including                 8131 1451
   coupled-channels (ECIS06 by J. Raynal)                         8131 1451
