   represents a good approximation to the DSD model               8131 1451
 - Exciton model with Iwamoto-Harada cluster                      8131 1451
   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 8131 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                8131 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   8131 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                8131 1451
   discrete transitions                                           8131 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL library [RIPL]                8131 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                8131 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               8131 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 8131 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 8131 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              8131 1451
   EXFOR/CSISRS library                                           8131 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A. Trkov)                    8131 1451
   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 8131 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                8131 1451
   PrePro codes by R. Cullen                                      8131 1451
